data.title: The Works of Benjamin Franklin, Vol. V Letters and Misc. Writings 1768-1772
data.meta_description: Volume 5 of a 12 volume collection of the works of Franklin edited by the New York lawyer and politician John Bigelow. Vol. 5 contains a essays and letters written between 1768 and 1772.
